Robert Halmi Inc said it obtained afive mln dlr line of revolving credit from Wells Fargo Bankavailable through February 29, 1988.    Halmi said the funds will be used for the development andproduction of television programming and for regular companybusiness.    Halmi said it reported earnings of 2,800,000 dlrs in fiscalyear 1986 ended May, 1986, on sales of 17.2 mln dlrs. Reuter&#3;